        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "🚀 Features"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "PageLM converts study material into **interactive resources** including quizzes, flashcards, structured notes, and podcasts.  \nThe platform provides a modern interface for students, educators, and researchers to **enhance learning efficiency** using state-of-the-art LLMs and TTS systems."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Learning Tools"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- **Contextual Chat** – Ask questions about uploaded documents (PDF, DOCX, Markdown, TXT)\n- **SmartNotes** – Generate Cornell-style notes automatically from topics or uploaded content\n- **Flashcards** – Extract non-overlapping flashcards for spaced repetition\n- **Quizzes** – Create interactive quizzes with hints, explanations, and scoring\n- **AI Podcast** – Convert notes and topics into engaging audio content for learning on the go\n- **Voice Transcribe** - Convert lecture recordings and voice notes into organized, searchable study materials instantly.\n- **Homework Planner** - Plans your Homework Smartly using AI, Assists if your stuck.\n- **ExamLab** - Simulate any exam, get feedback, and be prepared for the exam\n- **Debate** - Debate with AI to improve your Debate skills.\n- **Study Companion** - A personalised AI Companion that assists you."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Supported AI Models"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- Google Gemini • OpenAI GPT • Anthropic Claude • xAI Grok • Ollama (local) • OpenRouter"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Embedding Providers"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- OpenAI • Gemini • Ollama"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical Highlights"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- WebSocket streaming for real-time chat, notes, and podcast generation\n- JSON or vector database support for embeddings and retrieval\n- File-based persistent storage for generated content\n- Markdown-based outputs for structured answers and notes\n- Configurable multi-provider setup for LLMs and TTS engines"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "---"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "🛠️ Technology Stack"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "| Component      | Technology                               |\n| -------------- | ---------------------------------------- |\n| **Backend**    | Node.js, TypeScript, LangChain, Langraph |\n| **Frontend**   | Vite, React, TailwindCSS                 |\n| **Database**   | JSON (default), optional vector DB       |\n| **AI/ML**      | Multiple LLM providers, embeddings       |\n| **Audio**      | Edge TTS, ElevenLabs, Google TTS         |\n| **Deployment** | Docker, Docker Compose                   |\n| **Docs**       | pdf-lib, mammoth, pdf-parse              |"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "---"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "⚡ Getting Started"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Prerequisites"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- Node.js v21.18+\n- npm or pnpm\n- ffmpeg (required for podcast audio)\n- Docker (optional)"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Local Development"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeBlock",
          "attrs": {
            "language": "bash"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Clone the repository\ngit clone https://github.com/caviraOSS/pagelm.git"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Linux:\n  chmod 777 ./setup.sh\n  ./setup.sh"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Windows:\n  Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser\n  ./setup.ps1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Manual (Both Linux/Windows):\n  # Install dependencies\n  cd backend\n  npm install\n  cd ../frontend\n  npm install"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Setup environment\n  cd ..\n  npm i -g nodemon\n  cp .env.example .env\n  # Make sure to configure API keys and settings in .env"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Run these two commands in separate terminals but inside the project directory.\n  # Run backend\n  cd backend\n  npm run dev"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Run frontend\n  cd frontend\n  npm run dev\n```"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "👉 Access at: **http://localhost:5173**"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Docker Deployment"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeBlock",
          "attrs": {
            "language": "bash"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Development"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "# Production\ndocker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d --build\n```"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- Frontend: http://localhost:5173 (dev) / http://localhost:8080 (prod)\n- Backend: http://localhost:5000"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "---"
