          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "⚙️ Configuration"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "All configuration is handled via environment variables:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "- **LLM Provider** – Choose your model backend\n- **TTS Engine** – Select speech service for podcasts\n- **Database Backend** – JSON or vector DB\n- **File Upload Limits** – Customize size/format limits"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "See `.env.example` for all options."
            }
          ]
        },
